# install emacs:
Mac: brew install emacs
Linux: sudo apt-get install emacs
# Keys:
C : control
M: <alt> in Linux, <option> in Mac (if option does not work, use Esc instead)
# If the minibuffer command color is blue and hard to read, create a file with name .emacs in ~/, add the following line:
(set-face-foreground 'minibuffer-prompt "white")

